\begin_layout Itemize
for any pair of objects 
\begin_inset Formula $A,B\in\Obj(\hat{\mathsf{S}})$
\end_inset

 let 
\begin_inset Formula $\Hom_{\catC}(A,B)$
\end_inset

 be the pair 
\begin_inset Formula $(A,B)$
