\end_inset

 and so 
\begin_inset Formula $(hg)f=(A,D)=h(gf)$
\end_inset

.
 So,
 associativity also holds.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
That 
\begin_inset Formula $A\overset{f}{\longrightarrow}B$
\end_inset

